CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Risk object. This set defines the risk fields (if associated risks exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not displayed during creation of the project. No default field set is defined.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of a field set used by the Risk object. Fields in this set define the Risk fields (if associated risks exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not shown on the Create Project from Template page.
CustomField.label: Risk Hidden
